that group.

```
$nums = new Map(range(0, 9));
$part = $nums->partition(function ($value, $key) {
   return 0 == $value % 2 ? 'even' : 'odd';
});
var_dump(
    $part['odd']->count(), // 5
    array_sum($part['even']->toArray()) // 20
);
```

